==To set the time signature of a sequence==

'''1.''' Open the '''Change Meter''' window ( '''Project / Modify Conductor Track / Change Meter''' ).

'''2.''' Add the new meter by directly typing in the meter you want in the '''Change Meter'''.

'''3.''' You can now specify the start and end locations for the meter changes. To change the entire sequence meter set the From Measure value to 1 and set the To setting to end of sequence. If you want to add a Meter change mid sequence simply specify the start and end points

'''4.''' Choosing '''Only move bar lines''' will leave any existing data within the sequence unaffected. 

'''5.''' Click Change and close the window 


